<s docid="SJMN91-06256107" num="14" wdcount="11"> Two pivotal members of the 14-member committee -- Howell Heflin, D-Ala.</s>
<s docid="SJMN91-06256107" num="15" wdcount="5"> , and Arlen Specter, R-Pa.</s>
